}

import navbar from "./components/Common/Toolbar.vue";
import router from "./router";

export default {
    name: "App",

    computed: {
        showMenu() {
            if(this.$route.name == "login" ){
                return false;
            }
            else{
                return true;
            }

    mounted() {
         
          this.$session.start();
      if (this.$session.has("token")) {
        console.log(this.$session);
        
      }
  }
